content: lalalune: Led a major refactoring effort with an open PR (#2124) to remove plugins from core, modifying 1,962 files (+37,485/-120,778 lines) across 10 commits. Created 4 issues (#235, #226, #206, #2123) related to this effort, all of which were closed, while maintaining consistent activity on 5 out of 7 days. Contributed comments on 2 issues as part of this substantial codebase reorganization, with work primarily focused on code (52%) and configuration files (28%).
